main event: A witness saw a green-colored disk, tan in outline, the size of a car, while looking through a window in Chicago, Illinois on September 12, 1961.
interesting points: The object had a muffled hum, sounding like an aircraft.
The object had a tan color, and one light came on, oscillating.
The edges of the object were sharply outlined.
The witness was in their automobile when they noticed the object moving rapidly overhead through the hazy sky, changing direction and speed several times.
The object was seen by numerous observers and broke into two parts before disappearing.
sighted object: Green-colored disk, tan outline, size of a car
